---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now" description="Current engineering work, learning focus, experiments, and open-source priorities.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-page px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[var(--accent)]">Current state</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-normal sm:text-5xl">Now</h1>
    <div class="mt-10 max-w-reading notebook-panel rounded-md p-6">
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg leading-8 text-[var(--muted)]">
        <li>Building a Redis clone in Rust with RESP parsing, async networking, and pub/sub.</li>
        <li>Reading <cite>Designing Data-Intensive Applications</cite>.</li>
        <li>Exploring vector database internals with RocksDB, KD-Tree indexing, and KNN search.</li>
        <li>Working through emulator architecture, instruction decoding, and low-level graphics loops.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
